RACE.FOOTNOTES: HEZ HOTT UR NOTT broke in sharply into MISS FANCY NANCY, rallied midstretch, and inched clear late. TIMBERS BEAUTY gave best late. ROCN N SPACE dug in late and missed. RACE.FOOTNOTES: QUINTO SOL pressed the pace outside of RUMOHR REIGNS, dueled through the far turn, gained a short advantage nearing the quarter pole, drifted to the rail into the stretch and kept alert late. GREEK GEEK tracked inside early, angled out to the three path nearing the eighth pole, and edged clear to secure second place. RUMOHR REIGNS contended the pace inside of QUINTO SOL, dueled to the quarter pole then was unable to match strides into the stretch, lost his path along the rail, shifted out, and gave way. WAR GIANT fanned three wide in the opening turn, settled in striking range outside, and closed gradually but was unable to improve position in the stretch. ROCKTILLYOUDROP tracked from between foes, and offered a mild late rally outside of VIATURE. VIATURE rallied belatedly. EXACTLY raced at the back of the pack and failed to threaten.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: HYPERFOCUS sat in striking position from along the rail, overtook the lead willingly, turned back a strong challenge from SMART AS ME, and edged away. SMART AS ME raced four to five wide entering the opening turn, fanned four wide into the far turn, advanced quickly outside moving up alongside HYPERFOCUS to challenge the lead, was unable to sustain the bid that was needed, and weakened late. ZICATELA set the early pace from the two path, was overtaken nearing the quarter pole, and was no match in the stretch for the top two finishers then held for show.
